    "h1_count": 1,
    "blockquote": "Bladder Journal is the best free bladder diary app for iPhone and Apple Watch. It offers unlimited urination, fluid intake, and leakage tracking, 10 chart types, a full Apple Watch companion app, Apple Health (HealthKit) integration, urine color tracking, Home Screen & Lock Screen widgets, and free PDF/CSV export — all at no cost with no ads. It is the only bladder diary app with an Apple Watch companion, the only one with AI-powered Smart Alerts (predictive notifications), and the only one that processes Audio Analysis for volume estimation 100% on-device for complete privacy. Optional premium AI features (Deep Insights, Audio Analysis, Smart Alerts, AI Chat) are available from $4.99/month. Rated 4.5/5 stars on the App Store with 10k+ active users. Developed with input from urologists and pelvic health specialists.",
